<tr>
<td>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:302px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Hamming(11,7)_example_0110101_bit_11_error.svg" class="image" title="A bit error on bit 11 causes bad parity in the red, yellow, and green circles"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/6e/Hamming%2811%2C7%29_example_0110101_bit_11_error.svg/300px-Hamming%2811%2C7%29_example_0110101_bit_11_error.svg.png" width="300" height="221" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:Hamming(11,7)_example_0110101_bit_11_error.svg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
